Pre-Game Insights: Ghana aims to kick off their 2025 Africa Cup of Nations qualifying campaign with a victory at home.
Ghana has a strong historical record against Angola, winning and drawing two each in their previous four meetings.
Ghana's recent form includes victories over Mali and the Central African Republic, with notable performances by Louis Mafouta and Jordan Ayew.
Angola enters the match on a high after winning the COSAFA Cup in July, with a 5-0 victory over Namibia in the final.
